=Analyze the following article title and summary/content.

Title: {{ $json.title }}
Content: {{ $json.contentSnippet || $json.content || '' }}

Task:
1. Score relevance to "Artificial Intelligence" and "Software Development" from 0 to 100.
2. Write a concise summary (3-4 sentences).

Output Valid JSON:
{
"score": 85,
"summary": "..."
}

